{"tid":17765,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚福音！科學家：不做愛，可令人長壽","createTime":"2016-12-02T03:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T04:39:30.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08d2c0b9c8ca51e967ef0271e420dea750feefdf","tid":17765,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:06:47.000Z","msg":"英國一名36歲科學家札佛隆科夫(Alex Zhavoronkov)近日表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果人類想要長命百歲，活到150歲，「這輩子最好都不要做愛」。</span><br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，札佛隆科夫說，做愛、婚姻、養兒、享受物質都是阻礙長壽的因素，讓人分心，如果能摒除這些因子，人類就能活得長長久久。他在新書《不老的一代》(Ageless Generation)中指出，沒有性愛的生活，人類可以活得「很遠，很長久」。至於札佛隆科夫有沒有性生活？他說：「我偶爾做愛，但不是永久的基礎，我都跟其他科學家做。」他也指出，做愛後的互動其實很無聊。"},{"pid":"b7a15431191bcf78fdd0b6dc3393b6bd0d3cc5c6","tid":17765,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:08:00.000Z","msg":"冇得做愛咁長壽咪仲痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac741788ba16b1a4258dd046b78116664c76b369","tid":17765,"uid":19002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:08:55.000Z","msg":"個人長壽，人類短壽"},{"pid":"f8daa3540788973f1e0f72293ddac02bead83793","tid":17765,"uid":49267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:09:12.000Z","msg":"要咁長命做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68fa5e565dde1aa752bb0fba879d50079661905b","tid":17765,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:19:07.000Z","msg":"英國研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11b54c403b0861d0c39618b919931e6c8c9f68b","tid":17765,"uid":4302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:37:16.000Z","msg":"我屌埋你地個份<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131fc42d8f91f19ed5a8b84884ef242b4ec86028","tid":17765,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:38:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英國研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/